Jeremy London https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeremy_London 0 Jeremy Michael London (born November 7, 1972) is an American actor. He is best known for his regular roles on Party of Five, 7th Heaven, and I'll Fly Away, a starring role the 1995 comedy film Mallrats, as well as a notable supporting role in the Civil War epic Gods and Generals. London made his directorial debut with the 2013 horror film The Devil's Dozen, in which he also appeared. Jeremy_Michael_London ( born November_7_,_1972 ) is an_American_actor .
